    • Method Detail

      • getIdentifier

        public int getIdentifier()
        The identifier for this payload.

        The Payload Identifier is a unique BER-OID integer sequentially assigned starting with the number zero (0). The Active Payload (Item 139) uses the Payload Identifier to specify which payloads are active.

        Returns:
        the identifier.

      • setIdentifier

        public void setIdentifier(int identifier)
        Set the identifier for this payload.

        The Payload Identifier is a unique BER-OID integer sequentially assigned starting with the number zero (0). The Active Payload (Item 139) uses the Payload Identifier to specify which payloads are active.

        Parameters:
        identifier - the zero index payload identifier.

      • getType

        public int getType()
        The type of this payload.

        The Payload Type is a BER-OID enumeration. Valid values are 0 for Electro Optical MI Sensor; 1 for LIDAR; 2 for RADAR; 3 for SIGINT; 4 for SAR.

        Returns:
        the payload type as an integer enumeration value.

      • setType

        public void setType(int type)
        Set the type of this payload.

        The Payload Type is a BER-OID enumeration. Valid values are 0 for Electro Optical MI Sensor; 1 for LIDAR; 2 for RADAR; 3 for SIGINT; 4 for SAR.

        Parameters:
        type - the payload type as an integer enumeration value.
